import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import {AppBreadcrumbService} from '../app.breadcrumb.service'; @Component({ templateUrl: './app.help.component.html', }) export class AppHelpComponent { text: any; filteredText: any[]; constructor(private breadcrumbService: AppBreadcrumbService) { this.breadcrumbService.setItems([ {label: 'Pages'}, {label: 'Help Page'} ]); } filterText(event) { const query = event.query; this.filteredText = []; for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) { this.filteredText.push(query + i); } } }
